Clubs: {26 members of 21 homes belong {to a club or organisation.}
Eight of these were exclusively village related e.g. Parish Council or Playingfield Committees, various Church Committees and Clubs, Flower Club, Over Sixties Club and Youth Club. Other clubs were village run sections of national organisations e.g. Women's Institute, British Legion, Cub Scouts and Brownies. Only 7 respondents travelled either to Bognor or Chichester to attend clubs, which included Film Club, Drama or Singing Groups, Twin's Club, Ornithology Club and MIND.
